begin_memory_text: A little awkward at first , the connection was really dragging so the delay was significant. I had to really turn up my volume to hear. The picture was a little cloudy  and I had been in a hurry to make on time so I was a little flustered but worked out the quirks pretty quickly.
middle_memory_text: Well, we were telling each other of our home and the general feel of that , I was asked about what I did for fun and mentioned I was flying so my fun had ended. So I again told my favorite scenario of the trumpet Moroni dropped during our earthquake. We also talked about getting this pandemic over with by staying home and not messing around with it anymore.
end_memory_text: How his children perceived what was going on and the impact upon their psyche was interesting and I mentioned how much I think they have a different opinion of the world around them seemed to hit home. I felt he worried about them. We seemed to have the same view of how crazy  the political energy was messing up our lives.
rest_of_day_open:
